Best conceptual formula

Here’s the compressed invariant:

Visible structure = residue of repeated constraint + choice over time

RTFIE is the engine that tries to reverse that residue into:
	•	likely pressures
	•	likely events
	•	likely use-patterns
	•	likely timelines

That’s the clean version of “real-time AI anthropology and archaeology in one.”

